#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:2
msgid "ION Discover DJ"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:5
msgid ""
"The ION Discover DJ is a cheap budget MIDI controller meant to “discover DJ-"
"ing” for people with a potential interest. It does not have a built in sound"
" card, so a {ref}`splitter cable <hardware-splitter-cables>` or "
"{ref}`separate audio interface <hardware-audio-interfaces>` is required to "
"use headphones with it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:7
msgid ""
"[Forum thread](https://mixxx.discourse.group/t/ion-discover-dj-controller-"
"possible-future-support/10284)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:11
msgid "Compatibility"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:14
msgid ""
"This controller is USB MIDI class compliant, so it is plug-and-play on all "
"platforms without having to install any special drivers. The manufacturer’s "
"page only mentions Windows and Mac but it’s confirmed working on Linux as "
"well."
msgstr ""

