#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:29
msgid "Jog wheels"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:32
msgid ""
"The button in the center can be used to switch the jog wheels between search"
" and scratch mode. In search mode, the jog wheels can be used to seek to "
"different parts of a song when paused. When that deck is playing, the jog "
"wheels can be pushed/pulled to speed up/slow down the playback. This is "
"useful for beatmatching."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:35
msgid ""
"Pressing the center button will put the jog wheels in scratch mode, which "
"means that the deck in Mixxx will follow the absolute movement of the jog "
"wheels. In this mode the Scratch button is lit."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:37
msgid "Equalizers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:40
msgid ""
"This controller only has a 2-band equalizer but Mixxx uses a 3-band EQ. "
"Therefore, the volume knob has been mapped to the low EQ, the bass knob has "
"been mapped to the mid EQ, and the treble knob has been mapped to the high "
"EQ. For controlling the volume of the decks, use the crossfader."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:43
msgid "Other buttons"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/ion_discover_dj.md:46
msgid ""
"The pitch buttons will control the tempo which also controls the pitch, "
"except when keylock is on (padlock icon on screen)."
msgstr ""

